Package org.neo4j.cypher.internal.javacompat

Class SnapshotExecutionEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.cypher.internal.javacompat.ExecutionEngine
      • org.neo4j.cypher.internal.javacompat.SnapshotExecutionEngine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QueryExecutionEngine
    public class SnapshotExecutionEngine
extends ExecutionEngine
    ExecutionEngine engine that will try to run cypher query with guarantee that query will never see any data that coming from transaction that are newer then transaction that was the last closed on a moment when VersionContext was initialised. Observed behaviour is the same as executing query on top data snapshot for that version.
